name: Arrow Dodging
tooltip: Values greater than 0 allow user to teleport to dodge projectiles.

name: Breath Capacity
tooltip: Affects maximum value of air.

name: Breath Recovery
tooltip: Affects rate at which air is gained outside of water. Cleaved into one fourth of its value while sprinting. 0.5 breath prevents air gain and anything lower causes air loss.

name: Buff Purging
tooltip: Reduces duration of beneficial status effects from eating or drinking.

name: Buoyancy
tooltip: Applies a constant force to Y velocity, of 0.02 * buoyancy per tick.

name: Carnivorous Digestion
tooltip: Affects how many hunger shanks meat items restore. Meat items are food items that can be fed to wolves.

name: Carnivorous Nutrition
tooltip: Affects how many saturation points meat items restore. Meat items are food items that can be fed to wolves.

name: Creepy
tooltip: Ability. Allows player user to self-destruct, with explosion size based on Explosive organ score.

name: Crystalsynthesis
tooltip: Connects to nearby end crystals to restore hunger, then saturation, then health. Greater scores increase frequency.

name: Defense
tooltip: Reduces incoming damage. By default, 4 defense halves incoming damage.

name: Destructive Collisions
tooltip: Unused, does nothing

name: Detoxification
tooltip: Reduces duration of harmful status effects from eating or drinking.

name: Digestion
tooltip: Affects how many hunger shanks food items restore.

name: Dragon Bombs
tooltip: Ability. Allows player user to shoot dragon fireballs.

name: Dragon Breath
tooltip: Ability. Allows player user to shoot dragon breath.

name: Ease of Access
tooltip: Values greater than 0 prevent damage taken from the chest opener, and allow user's chest to be opened at any health.

name: Endurance
tooltip: Reduces exhaustion gain from all sources.

name: Explosive
tooltip: Statistic. Increases size of explosion from Creepy.

name: Filtration
tooltip: Values less than default will affect user with poison. Lower values increase duration.

name: Fire Resistance
tooltip: Reduces damage taken from fire. By default, 4 fire resistance quarters incoming fire damage.

name: Forceful Spit
tooltip: Ability. Allows player user to fire llama spit projectiles.

name: Furnace Powered
tooltip: Ability. Allows player user to consume fuel to gain a hunger restoration over time effect.

name: Ghastly
tooltip: Ability. Allows player user to fire ghast fireballs.

name: Glowing
tooltip: Values greater than 0 grant user the glowing effect.

name: Grazing
tooltip: Ability. Allows player user to convert grass blocks to dirt blocks for a hunger restoration over time effect.

name: Health
tooltip: Affects user's maximum health. By default, 1 health corresponds to 2 hearts.

name: Herbivorous Digestion
tooltip: Affects how many hunger shanks non-meat items restore. Meat items are food items that can be fed to wolves.

name: Herbivorous Nutrition
tooltip: Affects how many saturation points non-meat items restore. Meat items are food items that can be fed to wolves.

name: Hydroallergenic
tooltip: Damages user in water.

name: Hydrophobia
tooltip: Teleports user out of water.

name: Impact Resistant
tooltip: Reduces fall damage taken. By default, 4 impact resistance quarters incoming fall damage.

name: Incompatibility
tooltip: Internally used organ score. Determines organ rejection.

name: Iron Repair
tooltip: Ability. Allows player used to consume iron ingots or iron scrap to heal by a default of 25% of maximum health.

name: Knockback Resistant
tooltip: Reduces knockback taken.

name: Launching
tooltip: Applies a vertical force to attacked entities of a default of 0.1 * launching.

name: Leaping
tooltip: Affects jump height.

name: Lightweight
tooltip: Positive values reduce gravity, negative values apply more gravity.

name: Luck
tooltip: Affects user luck. In vanilla, luck changes loot from loot tables with quality attributes and bonus rolls, which is most commonly a fishing feature.

name: Metabolism
tooltip: Affects rate at which hunger and saturation are converted to health for natural healing.

name: Nerves
tooltip: Total values less than or equal to 0 prevent user from moving. Affects player user's mining and attack speed.

name: Nutrition
tooltip: Affects how many saturation points food items restore.

name: Photosynthesis
tooltip: Grants hunger restoration over time based on light level. By default, 8 photosynthesis in direct sunlight restores hunger every 50 ticks.

name: Spits Fire
tooltip: Ability. Allows player user to fire blaze fireballs.

name: Rot Digestion
tooltip: Affects how many hunger shanks rotten flesh items restore. If the sum of rotgut and rot digestion is greater than 0, player users may eat rotten food without risk of hunger.

name: Rotgut
tooltip: Affects how many saturation points rotten flesh items restore. If the sum of rotgut and rot digestion is greater than 0, player users may eat rotten food without risk of hunger.

name: Shoots Bullets
tooltip: Ability. Allows player user to fire homing shulker bullets.

name: Produces Silk
tooltip: Ability. Allows player user to create string, cobwebs, and/or wool.

name: Speed
tooltip: Affects movement speed of user.

name: Strength
tooltip: Affects attack damage of user.

name: Swim Speed
tooltip: Affects movement speed of user while in water.

name: Venomous
tooltip: Venom gland's ability. Inflicts attacked targets with corresponding status effect when punched with bare hand.

name: Water Breath
tooltip: Affects rate at which air is gained inside of water. Cleaved into one fourth of its value while sprinting. 0.5 breath prevents air gain or loss and anything lower causes air loss.

name: Withered
tooltip: Reduces duration of wither from wither roses.
